channel.desc: Comedy, Romance, Drama 2009 What was once a strong friendship between Emma and Olivia begins to crumble when their wedding plans overlap. Neither willing to change the date, they embark on a mission to sabotage each other's ceremonies. Anne Hathaway, Kate Hudson, Candice Bergen, Bryan Greenberg, Chris Pratt, Greg DePaul, Gary Winick.
